title: Homeinns Hotel Group to Report Third Quarter 2015 Financial Results on November 9, 2015Travelandtourworld.com
text:
Homeinns Hotel Group to Report Third Quarter 2015 Financial Results on November 9, 2015
Homeinns Hotel Group (“Homeinns” or “the Company”), a leading economy hotel chain in China, today announced that it will report its financial results for the third quarter 2015 on Monday November 9, 2015 after the U.S. market closes.
Management of Homeinns will hold an earnings conference call on Monday, November 9, 2015 at 8 PM U.S. Eastern Time (Tuesday, November 10, 2015 at 9 AM Beijing/Hong Kong time).
